title: Riot Kayle/Mystery Gift
body: About the rewards for the 5 year anniversary, i already own the riot kayle skin but i hadn't got my mystery gift skin yet. Has anyone got theirs? Just wanted to know if anyone has got it.

replies.body:
Hey there,

To my knowledge these are still being rolled out.

If you still haven't received anything by the 24th I'd recommend you to [submit a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/requests/new) to Player Support to take a look at.
